title: #441 - Mickey Gall
description:
Mickey Gall, a UFC Welterweight, perhaps soon to be lightweight, fighter, seen on "Dana White: Lookin' For A Fight" and as the first UFC opponent of CM Punk, joins Joey Diaz and Lee Syatt live in studio.
